12.description: The Howling Abyss is a bottomless crevasse located in the coldest, cruelest, part of the Freljord. Legends say that, long ago, a great battle took place here on the narrow bridge spanning this chasm. No one remembers who fought here, or why, but it is said that if you listen carefully to the wind you can still hear the cries of the vanquished tossed howling into the Abyss.
12.gameModeDescription: Ten randomly-selected champions assemble on a narrow bridge in a frozen land. Cross to the other side and destroy everything in your path.
12.name: Howling Abyss

22.description: Assemble a squad of champions that battle on your behalf. Outlast all seven of your opponents and become the last person standing.
22.gameModeDescription: Assemble a squad of champions that battle on your behalf. Outlast all seven of your opponents and become the last person standing.
22.name: Teamfight Tactics

locStrings.tutorial_subheader: Teamfight Tactics is a free-for-all drafting tactics game in which you recruit powerful champions, deploy them, and battle to become the last player standing. Here's a quick guide.

item1.body: Buy 2-star champs from the Shop that grant +1 towards a Trait and a unique bonus!

item2.body: Create powerful boards from iconic League bands like K/DA and Pentakill, plus new favorites!

item3.body: Vote on portals at the beginning of each game to bend the rules in your favor!

tutorialCards.description:
Choose a champion from the store and recruit them with gold. Then, drag them from the bench to the battlefield to deploy them.

Combine three of the same champion to create a stronger, two-star version of that champion.

Champions have traits and earn bonuses when deployed with other champs that share those traits.

Positioning matters! Experiment with different layouts to find the best results.

Each round, your team teleports to an enemy's arena (or vice-versa). Champions fight automatically, and if your team is defeated, your Tactician takes damage.

When your Tactician's health reaches 0, you're out of the game.

locStrings.tutorial_subheader: Hyper Roll is Teamfight Tactics, but shorter! The stakes are high every round!

tutorialCards.description: You start with 20 life; each loss will cost you two. But as the game goes on, losses will hurt more and more!
No more spending gold on XP - instead, you level up at the start of each Stage
There's no extra gold from interest in Hyper Roll, and no streak gold either - focus on building the best team you can!

22.name: Teamfight Tactics

tutorialCards.description: Invite a friend, or queue up solo. You and your partner will share a health pool and work together to beat out three other pairs. The last team standing wins!
If you beat your opponent before your partner beats theirs, your team will teleport to your partner's board to help them out.
Use the Assist Armory to gift your partner items and other goodies. Drag a Rune of Allegiance onto a champion to send them to your partner.

locStrings.tutorial_subheader: Train up and win the tournament!

tutorialCards.description: Health is replaced with Soul Power! During training you cannot die. Focus on building your Soul Power with Soul Fighter Gwen and Sett's help.
Champions given the Soul Crown item have increased power and bonus trait contribution. The Tournament unlocks a third Soul ability!
Go all out in the tournament phase. Each round is a best 2 of 3 with your opponent where only the winner moves on!

tutorialCards.description: Time to live large! Start the match with a powerful Tier 4 or Tier 5 champion to form the core of your team.
Choncc to the rescue! When your health gets low, Choncc will arrive with a care package to give you a boost!
Items galore! After every carousel round, Choncc will visit to share an ever increasing amount of treasure!

tutorialCards.description: Play this classic set, where mechanized monstrosities and strange spacefarers clash in a battle of galactic proportions.
Seasoned stargazers, prepare to brave new celestial frontiers! New items, new augments, and balance changes mean new strategies.
Galaxies are now decided by voting! Unlock a universe of possibilities with these game-changing cosmic portals.

21.gameModeDescription: Venture to a long forgotten Ionian temple and destroy the enemy Nexus while completing a set of outrageous challenges—win the fight quickly, or the Nexus will do it for you!
21.name: Nexus Blitz

0.body: Race your Scuttlecrab to the finish line!

1.body: Face off the enemy team in a series of duels!

2.body: Take the enemy team's lives before they take yours!

3.body: Fight for survival in a random Bardle Royale event!

4.body: Defeat the enemy team's Soraka before they defeat yours!

5.body: Do more damage to the Target Dummy than your opponents can!

6.body: Kill Loot Teemo for his bounty!

tutorialCards.description: Fights constantly break out on a compact map with special events and rewards adding a touch of chaos.
Roam as two junglers to share gold, XP, and buffs when clearing camps together.
Kill and assist hotstreaks set you on fire, making you much stronger—but also easier to kill.

locStrings.tutorial_subheader: Our long anticipated game mode is finally here!

tutorialCards.description: Queue up solo or team up with your closest friends in our new 8-player lobby. You can crush your enemies or your friends in this multi-team game mode.
Build your arsenal with over 150+ game-changing augments. Mix and match different combinations to overwhelm the other teams or strengthen yours.
Expand your strategies in the Arena. Heal with power flowers, pick up a fallen ally, travel with hex gates, and more! Can you and your ally claim victory?
